      <title>Go 调 OpenAI API 常见超时链路排查：DNS/TLS/代理/连接池一次讲清</title>
      <link>https://www.mfun.ink/2026/03/02/go-openai-api-timeout-troubleshooting-dns-tls-proxy-connection-pool/</link>
